      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STATUE OF TIME (5) has an excellent record here having never missed the placings in five starts, including four wins. Comes off a (30.44) win last time, scoring by 1.5 lengths in a Grade 5 over 530m at Angle Park. Appeals as a leading chance in this. SOLO MAN (7) looks close to win after hitting the frame last run (22.22) at this track in a Grade 3/4/5. Has first look at box 7 this time. Form at the trip sound including two wins. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Leading chance. SON OF MAPLE (1) is a fast beginner but out of character last time when always well back and missed the placings, finishing seventh (19.52) in a OPEN at this track. Prior to that was quickly into stride and scored (19.52) at this track. Solid record here at the distance winning five races. The form out of his last race has been franked. Cannot be left out. YUMALI (3) placed in impressive time last start - cannot be ignored.",
